'''歐洲主權債務危機'''，簡稱'''歐債危機'''，是指自2009年年底之后，不少財政上相對保守的投資者對部份[[歐洲|歐洲]]國家在[[主權債務危機|主權債務危機]]方面所產生的憂慮，危機在2010年年初的時候一度陷入最嚴峻的局面。<ref>{{Cite news |url= http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSLDE61F0W720100216 |title= Peripheral euro zone government bond spreads widen |agency= Reuters |author= George Matlock |date= 16 February 2010 |accessdate= 28 April 2010 |archive-date= 2019-12-14 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20191214170357/http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSLDE61F0W720100216 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.economist.com/node/16009099 | title=Acropolis now | work=The Economist | date=29 April 2010 | accessdate=22 June 2011 | archive-date=2017-10-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171020165642/http://www.economist.com/node/16009099 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

連串經濟危機和動盪中，被指出現問題的[[歐元區|歐元區]]國家包括[[希臘|希臘]]、<ref name=wsj>{{Cite news | author = Brian Blackstone, Tom Lauricella, and Neil Shah | title = Global Markets Shudder: Doubts About U.S. Economy and a Debt Crunch in Europe Jolt Hopes for a Recovery | work = The Wall Street Journal | date = 5 February 2010 | url = http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704041504575045743430262982.html | accessdate = 10 May 2010 | archive-date = 2010-05-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100502010951/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052748704041504575045743430262982.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]、[[義大利|義大利]]、[[西班牙|西班牙]]和[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]，合稱[[歐豬五國|歐豬五國]]的借貸信用降低國家，而部份不屬於歐元區國家的[[歐盟|歐盟]]成員國因為經濟連動之故也牽涉其中。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.thenewamerican.com/index.php/world-mainmenu-26/europe-mainmenu-35/3274-greek-debt-crisis-worsens |title=Greek Debt Crisis Worsens |author=Bruce Walker |date=9 April 2010 |publisher=The New American |accessdate=28 April 2010 |archive-date=2010-04-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100413065221/http://www.thenewamerican.com/index.php/world-mainmenu-26/europe-mainmenu-35/3274-greek-debt-crisis-worsens |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[冰島|冰島]]雖然在2008年遭遇當時全球規模最大的[[2008年冰島金融危機|金融危機]]，導致該國的國際銀行體系崩坍，但正因為冰島政府無力救助銀行脫險，主權債務危機對冰島帶來的影響反而較少。相反，針對那些為了出手救助銀行而導致主權債務急增的部份歐盟成員國而言，由於這些國家與其他歐盟成員國，特別是與[[德國|德國]]之間在[[債券|債券]][[收益率差價|收益率差價]]和[[信貸違約掉期|信貸違約掉期]]方面的差異愈來愈大，使得這些國家逐漸浮現信心危機。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.financialmirror.com/News/Cyprus_and_World_News/20151 |title=Greek/German bond yield spread more than 1,000 bps |publisher=Financialmirror.com |date=28 April 2010 |accessdate=5 May 2010 |archive-date=2020-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200601011441/http://www.financialmirror.com/News/Cyprus_and_World_News/20151 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/7d25573c-1ccc-11df-8d8e-00144feab49a.html |title=Gilt yields rise amid UK debt concerns |work=Financial Times |date=18 February 2010 |accessdate=15 April 2011 |archive-date=2015-01-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150120045444/http://www.ft.com/cms/s/0/7d25573c-1ccc-11df-8d8e-00144feab49a.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==救助方案==
關注到環球多國政府[[赤字|赤字]]和[[公債|負債]]水平不斷上升，<ref name="telegraph.co.uk">{{Cite news |title=Britain's deficit third worst in the world, table |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/financetopics/financialcrisis/7269629/Britains-deficit-third-worst-in-the-world-table.html |work=The Daily Telegraph |location=London |date=19 February 2010 |accessdate=29 April 2010 |archive-date=2010-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100222082519/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/financetopics/financialcrisis/7269629/Britains-deficit-third-worst-in-the-world-table.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.ft.com/money-supply/files/2010/01/misery.gif |title=Fiscal Deficit and Unemployment Rate, FT |accessdate=5 May 2010 |archive-date=2011-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111121235512/http://blogs.ft.com/money-supply/files/2010/01/misery.gif |dead-url=no }}</ref>再加上歐洲多國公債先後被降低評級，<ref>{{Cite news |title= Timeline: Greece's economic crisis |url= http://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6124EL20100203 |date= 3 February 2010 |accessdate= 29 April 2010 |agency= Reuters |archive-date= 2021-02-07 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210207053205/https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSTRE6124EL20100203 |dead-url= no }}</ref>使金融市場響起警號。在2010年5月9日，歐盟多國[[財政部長|財長]]通過一個總值7,500億[[歐元|歐元]]（相當於當時10,000億[[美元|美元]]）的全面救助計劃，用以成立一個[[歐洲金融穩定基金|歐洲金融穩定基金]]（EFSF），希望藉以確保歐洲整體的金融穩定。<ref name="BBC10052010">{{Cite news|url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/8671632.stm|title=EU ministers offer 750bn-euro plan to support currency |date=10 May 2010|publisher=BBC News |accessdate=11 May 2010}}</ref>

2010年發生的債務危機，主要源自希臘急於援用鉅額融資來設法支付大量到期公債，以避免出現債務違約的風險。有鑑於此，歐元區國家與[[國際貨幣基金會|國際貨幣基金會]]在2010年5月2日同意向希臘提供總值1,100億歐元貸款，但條件是希臘需要厲行一系列的[[緊縮開支措施|緊縮開支措施]]。<ref>{{Cite news |author=Gabi Thesing and Flavia Krause-Jackson |title=Greece Gets {{Nowrap|$146 Billion}} Rescue in EU, IMF Package |url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601087&sid=a9f8X9yDMcdI&pos=1 |publisher=Bloomberg |date=3 May 2010 |accessdate=10 May 2010 |archive-date=2010-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100411091541/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601087 |dead-url=no }}</ref>繼希臘以後，愛爾蘭在同年11月也獲得總值850億歐元的救助方案，<ref>Treanor, Jill and Elliott, Larry [http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2010/nov/24/ireland-loan-bailout-nationalise-banks Ireland to get €85bn loan in deal that will nationalise its banks] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/business/2010/nov/24/ireland-loan-bailout-nationalise-banks |date=20121109030731 }} The Guardian, 24 November 2010, Retrieved 19 May 2011</ref>而葡萄牙則在2011年5月獲得另一個總值780億歐元的援助。<ref name="Butler_The Daily Telegraph">{{cite news
 |url          = http://www.telegraph.co.uk/comment/columnists/christopherhowse/7482331/Sacred-Mysteries-Taking-the-God-out-of-good.html
